body:

------
I was curious about the popularity of chess variants at [https://lichess.org](https://lichess.org/).

So I grabbed the data from the lichess [game database](https://database.lichess.org/) and created some visualizations. I hope you enjoy them!

------


#### Overview
Let's start with a heatmap. You can hover over it with your mouse to see the exact number of games played of each variant in each month.
