In <a  href='https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Losing_Chess'> antichess </a> the objective is to <i>lose</i> all your peaces or reach a stalemate.


------
<a name="atomic"></a>
#### Atomic


<div>
<center>
<script
    src="bar_atomic.js"
    id="0d293427-76b9-4afa-95d7-cae0a254f5d7"
